abstract: >-
  A tool for extracting structured metadata from scientific posters, converting
  visual poster content into machine-actionable JSON format conforming to the
  poster-json-schema. Uses Qwen2-VL for image OCR and a fine-tuned Llama 3.1 8B
  for JSON structuring. Part of the posters.science platform.
